PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Communications of ROBERT K. ARMSTRONG, of Peterborough, Ontario, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Nature to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Susanne Hudson-French, who has resigned.
